{"tid":187944,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人頸痛 同埋睇過脊醫","createTime":"2017-04-05T10:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T16:30:16.000Z","uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7099adba8cc9c71ac250bc36bdddf7342a2fbfb0","tid":187944,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:27:03.000Z","msg":"睇緊佐敦一間 好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次講兩句已經收600<br />\n叫我去照X光 <br />\n照完睇報告都要600<br />\n之後每次仲要750 <br />\n<br />\n頸痛左4個月 照左X光發覺有少少歪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚想死"},{"pid":"27796bb66e8811ac29fa496d571e4aba503bf399","tid":187944,"uid":103687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:33:08.000Z","msg":"其實如果一伸懶腰/扭腰嘅時候 腰椎位啲骨會係咁啪啪聲<br />\n我條脊椎骨仲使唔使要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1716821035193bfb58528b588b5c923527860ff9","tid":187944,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:34:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實如果一伸懶腰/扭腰嘅時候 腰椎位啲骨會係咁啪啪聲<br />\n我條脊椎骨仲使唔使要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔知<br />\n我傷頸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇過跌打啪過骨都好似冇咩用<br />\n唯有試下瘠醫"},{"pid":"01c8a2a42aa9a2ee2152d15a02a92186d8a355b0","tid":187944,"uid":61965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:35:20.000Z","msg":"由6歲痛到19歲<br />\n今年先去左去排期做物理治療<br />\n等到8月頸都斷<br />\n巴打會唔會頸痛到頭都痛埋？"},{"pid":"82f504856108c01e6c245754f478ac4e546ab1bc","tid":187944,"uid":7353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:45:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dde484bbe622ab76a2aa647400d59c60acba67c6","tid":187944,"uid":7353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:46:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"681ce7624be5803393f2964be74b15f8b1e6a607","tid":187944,"uid":103687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:48:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實如果一伸懶腰/扭腰嘅時候 腰椎位啲骨會係咁啪啪聲<br />\n我條脊椎骨仲使唔使要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔知<br />\n我傷頸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇過跌打啪過骨都好似冇咩用<br />\n唯有試下瘠醫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n物理治療好撚煩㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你係勞損傷咗？"},{"pid":"019f50297091c8ff8a89b16a3fd91cef9557c358","tid":187944,"uid":61965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:51:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>由6歲痛到19歲<br />\n今年先去左去排期做物理治療<br />\n等到8月頸都斷<br />\n巴打會唔會頸痛到頭都痛埋？</blockquote><br />\n排到仆街啦呢D<br />\n呢d 唔會睇一次就好<br />\n起碼要睇幾次<br />\n買份保險claim 睇私人仲快</blockquote><br />\n父親份工有得claim 70%<br />\n但我唔知我呢啲屬於咩？<br />\n去私家醫院睇？要轉介信？"},{"pid":"89c5ac3860e2c01336bbf5492cbc6cc708c8773e","tid":187944,"uid":19641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:57:56.000Z","msg":"脊醫冇用<br />\n之前條頸好緊唔係好郁到<br />\n睇左中環出名脊醫5,6次都完全冇進展<br />\n只後轉去睇西醫，荃灣肌骼科唔記得咩名既醫生<br />\n睇左2次就好返 (要食藥）<br />\n可能我係純粹肌肉太緊  唔係咩骨有事先咁快好<br />\n唔你你情況係點  但可以比你參考下"},{"pid":"f1ff899c7baebfda751dd738a0f39447cf6d261e","tid":187944,"uid":19641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T11:00:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>脊醫冇用<br />\n之前條頸好緊唔係好郁到<br />\n睇左中環出名脊醫5,6次都完全冇進展<br />\n只後轉去睇西醫，荃灣肌骼科唔記得咩名既醫生<br />\n睇左2次就好返 (要食藥）<br />\n可能我係純粹肌肉太緊  唔係咩骨有事先咁快好<br />\n唔你你情況係點  但可以比你參考下</blockquote><br />\nBtw  脊醫同我照過都係條頭唔正   佢話太直<br />\n叫我買個千幾蚊既拉頸器自己日日拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇買到但最後都好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b971712a96e0f6e97f86488d58c8c1b5252a26a8","tid":187944,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T11:03:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>脊醫冇用<br />\n之前條頸好緊唔係好郁到<br />\n睇左中環出名脊醫5,6次都完全冇進展<br />\n只後轉去睇西醫，荃灣肌骼科唔記得咩名既醫生<br />\n睇左2次就好返 (要食藥）<br />\n可能我係純粹肌肉太緊  唔係咩骨有事先咁快好<br />\n唔你你情況係點  但可以比你參考下</blockquote><br />\n有冇咩推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fcd7b6a2b74cb984f872245dc8866b2900f1f1f","tid":187944,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T11:03:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇緊佐敦一間 好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次講兩句已經收600<br />\n叫我去照X光 <br />\n照完睇報告都要600<br />\n之後每次仲要750 <br />\n<br />\n頸痛左4個月 照左X光發覺有少少歪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚想死</blockquote><br />\n佢一定會話你有少少歪<br />\n同埋呢D 佢會同你講個療治有三四個階段<br />\n起碼要睇成皮野</blockquote><br />\n我都覺得佢搶緊錢"},{"pid":"7c6a2af6fd108e905b4601d9065b6d11bc0b9627","tid":187944,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T11:17:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實如果一伸懶腰/扭腰嘅時候 腰椎位啲骨會係咁啪啪聲<br />\n我條脊椎骨仲使唔使要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔知<br />\n我傷頸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇過跌打啪過骨都好似冇咩用<br />\n唯有試下瘠醫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n物理治療好撚煩㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你係勞損傷咗？</blockquote><br />\n係"},{"pid":"9441110ea93692e9b7cbf380029f5e177af277a4","tid":187944,"uid":69778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T11:21:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實如果一伸懶腰/扭腰嘅時候 腰椎位啲骨會係咁啪啪聲<br />\n我條脊椎骨仲使唔使要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n肌肉太緊都可以導致啪啪聲 以前條頸係咁啪啪啪 原來歪咗 整番啱位冇再有聲 但條腰睇極都係啪 老咗實有腰患<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db9f1692e7b114e112fbef5edf1f4178841121bc","tid":187944,"uid":39276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T11:31:18.000Z","msg":"我之前都頸痛 痛到要戴勁箍瞓覺<br />\n睇過個脊醫 佢自己本身都係物理治療師<br />\n都睇左好耐先好返<br />\n治療個時佢都會同我做啲物理治療<br />\n不過都收得貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66aac05a898e7ec8018805c3c72ac497f7b18623","tid":187944,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T11:34:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我之前都頸痛 痛到要戴勁箍瞓覺<br />\n睇過個脊醫 佢自己本身都係物理治療師<br />\n都睇左好耐先好返<br />\n治療個時佢都會同我做啲物理治療<br />\n不過都收得貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n貴到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370b61ff44c3dc4573fb0654e61bec52dd07d22c","tid":187944,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe2da51e7a022ac78672cccdccf934e46e4b83c8","tid":187944,"uid":63211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:51:07.000Z","msg":"你係點痛法?"},{"pid":"80be85b3c09ee7a3306ac4fdd5c6dd0788f96270","tid":187944,"uid":5777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:57:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>脊醫冇用<br />\n之前條頸好緊唔係好郁到<br />\n睇左中環出名脊醫5,6次都完全冇進展<br />\n只後轉去睇西醫，荃灣肌骼科唔記得咩名既醫生<br />\n睇左2次就好返 (要食藥）<br />\n可能我係純粹肌肉太緊  唔係咩骨有事先咁快好<br />\n唔你你情況係點  但可以比你參考下</blockquote><br />\n巴打可唔可以比醫生名<br />\n除左食藥洗唔洗拉筋個d?"},{"pid":"6b64302076c89a7379bb6598d85ed3ef0414688a","tid":187944,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:57:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係點痛法?</blockquote><br />\n用力 一郁就痛 唔郁就咁冇事"},{"pid":"7a82d78bf987fe76d3549eaf3ca62e69fcfa0a40","tid":187944,"uid":19641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:29:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>脊醫冇用<br />\n之前條頸好緊唔係好郁到<br />\n